    "bio_summary": "Behdad Nejatbakhshe (a.k.a Uppermost, from Paris, France) was 17 when he discovered music production. He took his first steps through FL Studio and listened to artists like deadmau5, the Daft Punk duo or Rank-1, who brought him much inspiration. In the space of three years, he discovered the functionalities and tools of the program interface, and began his first production.  He then created a melodic style which defines every one of his compositions. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/Uppermost\"",
